<item>
            <title>[LU-6406] prevent stack overrun in some tests</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6406</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A Lustre filesystem name is up to 8 characters, plus 1 for the NUL terminator. If a filesystem name is 8 characters, then the llapi_layout_test, llapi_hsm_test and llapi_fid_test will scribble their stack or overrun it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
